snippet.title: Talisman | PlayStation Reveal Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Talisman really is coming to PlayStation! You’ve heard rumours in the past about it being released, well this time it’s really happening!

Nomad Games will bring Talisman to PlayStation 4 and PlayStation Vita and the release date is not far off – it's due in early spring 2017!
